{"tid":174913,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"他拿照片要剪油頭　結果髮型師剪成這樣","createTime":"2017-03-27T07:04:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-27T07:04:33.000Z","uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3121aeb68f9172a6b704c75b325a1541dc31d2d5","tid":174913,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T07:04:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170327/640_9f403452b47aba6475fb6df9bc81b1f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170327%2F640_9f403452b47aba6475fb6df9bc81b1f0.jpg&h=ee92bb4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網友說，他給髮型師看之前剪油頭的照片<br />\n<br />\n剪頭髮，還提供照片給髮型師參考，但沒想到網友的下場卻有點悲劇&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n網友說，他去台中豐原某家美容院剪髮，跟設計師說要剪油頭，設計師還反問『你知道什麼是油頭嗎？』網友於是將之前剪的油頭照片給髮型師參考，髮型師也點點頭說「我往這個方向發展」結果剪完後，網友坦言大傻眼！而其他網友看了他附的after照片也回「這是永澤嗎？」、「對不起，我笑了」、「這真的是洋蔥頭呀」、「超雷的」（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170327/420_030d59b0024059879584c7a75eb9ee64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170327%2F420_030d59b0024059879584c7a75eb9ee64.jpg&h=fa5dded3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n結果剪出來變這樣！翻攝ptt<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170327/420_5c09595b4dd964923a3dd5522144c5ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170327%2F420_5c09595b4dd964923a3dd5522144c5ab.jpg&h=df97d27a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n永澤，翻攝自youtube<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/life/20170327/1085287/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Flife%2F20170327%2F1085287%2F&d=s93SzOo3lOnuHTfFtNogbZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=49a83650\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/life/20170327/1085287/</a>"}]}